                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-container">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span class="accordion-btn-text">5. Why should plumbers choose Plumbpay over continuing to use traditional paper methods for their quotes and invoices?</span>
                    <svg class="accordion-icon" width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
